md:text-3xl","children":"Share Christ in villages and unreached communities."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-7 space-y-5 font-body text-base leading-8 text-[#5F575E]","children":[["$","p","A mission trip gives you the opportunity to stand with local pastors and proclaim the hope of Jesus Christ in places where many families are still waiting to hear the Good News clearly.",{"children":"A mission trip gives you the opportunity to stand with local pastors and proclaim the hope of Jesus Christ in places where many families are still waiting to hear the Good News clearly."}],["$","p","Teams may participate in village meetings, church services, open-air Gospel gatherings, personal prayer, testimony sharing, and encouragement visits. Every message is carried with humility, love, and partnership with local leaders who understand the people and culture.",{"children":"Teams may participate in village meetings, church services, open-air Gospel gatherings, personal prayer, testimony sharing, and encouragement visits. Every message is carried with humility, love, and partnership with local leaders who understand the people and culture."}],["$","p","The goal is not only to speak, but to serve: to pray for people, listen to their stories, strengthen believers, and point every heart to the Savior.",{"children":"The goal is not only to speak, but to serve: to pray for people, listen to their stories, strengthen believers, and point every heart to the Savior."}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 border-t border-[#B51657]/15 pt-6","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"font-[Playfair_Display] text-xl italic leading-relaxed text-[#1E1E22] md:text-2xl","children":"\"Go into all the world and preach the gospel to every creature.\""}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 font-accent text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[#B51657]","children":"Mark 16:15"}]]}]]}]]}]}],["$","$L2","Teach and Encourage Leaders",{"delay":90,"children":["$","article",null,{"className":"